snippet.title: [The Last Three] - Official Trailer | Epic Release December 2024
snippet.description:
Deep in a magical forest lives the last stone tiger family. They are the guardians of balance and the mystical creatures' realm. But their peace is shattered when dark forces invade and abduct the mother. The father and cub embark on a perilous journey to rescue her.

Coming in December 2024 to Windows, exclusively on the Epic Games store.

Add to Wishlist: http://bit.ly/3yQ8sME
